// 1- Install the plugin
// 2- Enable web service advance feature (Admin > Advanced features)
// 3- Enable REST and XMLRPC protocol (Admin > Plugins > Web services > Manage protocols)
// 4- (optional) Create a token for a specific user and for the service 'My service' (Admin > Plugins > Web services > Manage tokens). If you don't want to create a token, you can use a user's login credentials when configuring the node client.
// 5- Enable specific external services. We need 'Moodle Mobile Web Service' and 'My service' to be enabled. Click edit and then check the enable box